ca.mcgill.ecse211.dpm16

Class MainController

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.mcgill.ecse211.dpm16.MainController

  • public class MainController
extends java.lang.Object
    The main class that starts the motors, sensors and the localization process. After localization it starts the navigation process which in turn, starts the ring and color detection then call the grabber class to the Grab the ring.
    Author:
    Reem Madkour
